{"tid":2378067,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發時空・沈旭暉】 假如龐貝奧成為總統：中國制裁28名美國前高官之後","createTime":"2021-01-24T07:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T07:19:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f927248bee1cc7be840ee0640006da709a376b76","tid":2378067,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"【突發時空・沈旭暉034🇺🇸🇨🇳】<br />\n假如龐貝奧成為總統：中國制裁28名美國前高官之後<br />\nJan 22, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NsiCE0zGKB4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNsiCE0zGKB4&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCEWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=b416605a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NsiCE0zGKB4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n189K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n中國在特朗普政府離任後，第一時間制裁28名高官，名單排榜首的是龐貝奧，假如此事認真處理，後續可以充滿戲劇性。我們先作對比：美國制裁中國人大副委員長時，雖然級別甚高，但只是集中於美資銀行不能為他們提供服務等，未有觸及他們的子女（大概除了出入境），也未有觸及他們的所屬機構，否則整個人大就不可以和美國有任何接觸，而中國是單一整體，也就是變相中美交往全面停頓。但中國這次制裁，為了「大佢一倍」，不但有被制裁14人雙倍奉還為28人，還把所有招數都寫上：涉及其家屬，也影響其關聯企業、機構。這和美國制裁的精準構成很大對比。假如龐貝奧有機會當上總統，又會怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n⏺ 全文見Patreon <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/46486437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F46486437&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCEWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=4e3bb136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/46486437</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/46484262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F46484262&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCEWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=6a7a87ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/46484262</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/46469296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F46469296&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCEWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=9adc65e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/46469296</a><br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 So